results.cleanName: Zendikar Rising Commander Deck Set of 2

extendedData.name: OracleText
extendedData.value:
Commander isn't only one of the most popular Magic formats—it's also how a lot of people learn to play. Zendikar Rising Commander Decks are designed to make learning Magic through Commander a great experience for those new players.

These decks are the perfect onramp for folks diving into both Commander and Magic in general, taking the place of Planeswalker Decks for Zendikar Rising.

Contents of each deck:
• 99-card deck
• 1 foil Commander
• 10 double-sided tokens
• 1 deck box
• 1 Life Wheel
